<codeline><highlight class="normal">export<sp/>DOC_PATH=&quot;./my-docs&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Step<sp/>2:<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>-<sp/>If<sp/>you&apos;re<sp/>running<sp/>the<sp/>frontend<sp/>app<sp/>on<sp/>localhost:8000,<sp/>simply<sp/>select<sp/>&quot;My<sp/>Documents&quot;<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>the<sp/>&quot;Report<sp/>Source&quot;<sp/>Dropdown<sp/>Options.</highlight></codeline>
